text: Seagull Marine is one of the best engineering company in Singapore. Seagull is specialist in all kind of Marine and offshore steel working and repair . Seagull has their own machine shop with latest CNC machines with experienced Engineers and Technicians .
Good work shop, quality workmanship and product delivery on time.
Beware, this company fails to pay contractors for services rendered and moves around contractors so that they dont need to pay them on time.
All kinds of industrial steel works.
